dc_description_s: These data represent zoning for Burnett County, Wisconsin in 2020 and include the layers 'Burnett_Airport_2020', 'Burnett_General_2020', and 'Burnett_Shoreland_2020'. General: [The shapefile contains zoning information for townships in Burnett County that are zoned. It should be noted that even if a township has not adopted a zoning policy, land nearby watercourses in Burnett County is zoned. For more information on township zoning, please contact the Burnett County Land Use Office.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
